Name: Super Grower
About the game: Be agile and grow big to overcome this game. Beat 40 levels by being fast, eat yellow dots and grow bigger. If enemies are smaller than you, they turn green and you are able to eat them. Remove all enemies from the battle arena to win the level. The game gets gradually more hectic and thus harder.
